{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-18",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_18_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 18 - The Fall-Guy",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 4,
  "page_total": 9,
  "page_start_sec": 741.32,
  "page_end_sec": 983.9,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.691,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 741.32,
      "end": 742.1,
      "text": "Then you'll have to duck",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 742.1,
      "end": 742.88,
      "text": "for cover with it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 742.94,
      "end": 743.88,
      "text": "no matter where you are,"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.0,
      "end": 745.94,
      "text": "and that's not going to help you make your fortune"
    },
    {
      "start": 746.12,
      "end": 746.4,
      "text": "off it."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.6,
      "end": 749.91,
      "text": "Give them a Fall-Guy and they'll stop right there.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 750.7,
      "end": 751.52,
      "text": "\"'Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 751.56,
      "end": 751.86,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.04,
      "end": 753.792,
      "text": "that's just the point,'"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.432,
      "end": 755.08,
      "text": "Gutman replied,"
    },
    {
      "start": 755.38,
      "end": 758.0,
      "text": "and still only in his eyes was uneasiness"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.06,
      "end": 758.84,
      "text": "faintly apparent."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.064,
      "end": 761.4,
      "text": "\"'Will they stop right there?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 761.6,
      "end": 764.94,
      "text": "Or won't your Fall-Guy be a fresh clue that"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.04,
      "end": 767.48,
      "text": "as likely as not will lead them straight to the Falcon?"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.68,
      "end": 769.64,
      "text": "And on the other hand,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 769.66,
      "end": 770.21,
      "text": "wouldn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.4,
      "end": 772.38,
      "text": "you say that they were stopped right now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 772.67,
      "end": 774.58,
      "text": "and that the best thing for us to do is to"
    },
    {
      "start": 774.74,
      "end": 777.66,
      "text": "leave well enough alone?' A forked vein"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.66,
      "end": 779.68,
      "text": "began to swell in Spade's forehead."
    },
    {
      "start": 780.92,
      "end": 781.22,
      "text": "\"'Hm.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 781.72,
      "end": 783.42,
      "text": "You don't know what it's all about,"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.48,
      "end": 785.88,
      "text": "either,' he said in a restrained tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.12,
      "end": 787.72,
      "text": "\"'They're not asleep,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 787.98,
      "end": 788.26,
      "text": "Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 788.82,
      "end": 789.52,
      "text": "They're lying low,"
    },
    {
      "start": 789.64,
      "end": 789.98,
      "text": "waiting."
    },
    {
      "start": 790.74,
      "end": 791.44,
      "text": "Try to get that.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 792.224,
      "end": 793.28,
      "text": "I'm in it up to my neck",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 793.28,
      "end": 793.96,
      "text": "and they know it."
    },
    {
      "start": 795.392,
      "end": 797.92,
      "text": "That's all right as long as I do something when the time comes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 798.52,
      "end": 799.02,
      "text": "but it won't"
    },
    {
      "start": 799.12,
      "end": 800.48,
      "text": "be all right if I don't!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 800.86,
      "end": 803.3,
      "text": "His voice became persuasive again."
    },
    {
      "start": 804.17,
      "end": 804.92,
      "text": "\"'Listen,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 805.02,
      "end": 805.32,
      "text": "Gutman,"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.5,
      "end": 808.06,
      "text": "we've absolutely got to give them a victim."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.8,
      "end": 809.08,
      "text": "There's no",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 809.08,
      "end": 809.82,
      "text": "way out of it."
    },
    {
      "start": 811.072,
      "end": 812.18,
      "text": "Let's give them the punk.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 812.96,
      "end": 814.2,
      "text": "He nodded pleasantly at the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 814.24,
      "end": 814.92,
      "text": "boy in the doorway."
    },
    {
      "start": 815.82,
      "end": 817.86,
      "text": "He actually did shoot both of them,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 818.02,
      "end": 819.16,
      "text": "Thursby and Jacoby,"
    },
    {
      "start": 819.34,
      "end": 819.84,
      "text": "didn't he?"
    },
    {
      "start": 820.38,
      "end": 820.86,
      "text": "Anyway,"
    },
    {
      "start": 821.08,
      "end": 822.82,
      "text": "he's made to order for the part."
    },
    {
      "start": 823.776,
      "end": 824.72,
      "text": "Let's pin the necessary",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 824.78,
      "end": 827.296,
      "text": "evidence on him and turn him over to them.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 828.78,
      "end": 830.42,
      "text": "The boy in the doorway tightened the corners",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 830.42,
      "end": 832.58,
      "text": "of his mouth in what may have been a minute"
    },
    {
      "start": 832.88,
      "end": 833.1,
      "text": "smile."
    },
    {
      "start": 834.176,
      "end": 836.76,
      "text": "Spade's proposal seemed to have no other effect on him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 837.76,
      "end": 840.3,
      "text": "Joel Cairo's dark face was open-mouthed,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 840.3,
      "end": 840.92,
      "text": "open-eyed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 841.12,
      "end": 842.22,
      "text": "yellowish and amazed."
    },
    {
      "start": 842.752,
      "end": 843.92,
      "text": "He breathed through"
    },
    {
      "start": 843.92,
      "end": 844.4,
      "text": "his mouth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 844.56,
      "end": 847.4,
      "text": "his round effeminate chest rising and falling,"
    },
    {
      "start": 847.58,
      "end": 848.96,
      "text": "while he gaped at Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 850.432,
      "end": 852.3,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy had moved away from",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 852.3,
      "end": 854.4,
      "text": "Spade a little and had twisted herself around"
    },
    {
      "start": 854.56,
      "end": 856.08,
      "text": "on the sofa to stare at him."
    },
    {
      "start": 857.2,
      "end": 860.32,
      "text": "There was a suggestion of hysterical laughter behind the startled",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 860.42,
      "end": 861.66,
      "text": "confusion in her face."
    },
    {
      "start": 863.072,
      "end": 866.06,
      "text": "Gutman remained still and expressionless for a long moment.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 866.52,
      "end": 867.16,
      "text": "Then"
    },
    {
      "start": 867.34,
      "end": 868.36,
      "text": "he decided to laugh."
    },
    {
      "start": 869.12,
      "end": 871.06,
      "text": "He laughed heartily and lengthily,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 871.24,
      "end": 873.58,
      "text": "not stopping until his sleek eyes"
    },
    {
      "start": 873.58,
      "end": 875.44,
      "text": "had borrowed merriment from his laughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 876.66,
      "end": 878.0,
      "text": "When he stopped laughing he said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 878.7,
      "end": 879.38,
      "text": "\"'By gad,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 879.42,
      "end": 879.7,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 879.88,
      "end": 880.96,
      "text": "you're a character,"
    },
    {
      "start": 881.18,
      "end": 882.24,
      "text": "that you are!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 882.46,
      "end": 885.96,
      "text": "He took a white handkerchief from his pocket and wiped his eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 886.76,
      "end": 887.56,
      "text": "\"'Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 887.6,
      "end": 887.9,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.98,
      "end": 891.32,
      "text": "there's never any telling what you'll do or say next,"
    },
    {
      "start": 891.54,
      "end": 893.04,
      "text": "except that it's bound"
    },
    {
      "start": 893.04,
      "end": 894.56,
      "text": "to be something astonishing.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 896.704,
      "end": 898.4,
      "text": "\"'There's nothing funny about it.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 899.392,
      "end": 902.14,
      "text": "Spade did not seem offended by the fat man's laughter,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 902.36,
      "end": 903.88,
      "text": "nor in any way impressed."
    },
    {
      "start": 904.72,
      "end": 907.02,
      "text": "He spoke in the manner of one reasoning with",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 907.02,
      "end": 909.32,
      "text": "a recalcitrant but not altogether unreasonable"
    },
    {
      "start": 909.8,
      "end": 910.1,
      "text": "friend."
    },
    {
      "start": 911.84,
      "end": 912.68,
      "text": "\"'It's our best bet.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 913.36,
      "end": 914.4,
      "text": "With him in their hands,"
    },
    {
      "start": 914.56,
      "end": 915.4,
      "text": "the police will—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 915.74,
      "end": 916.06,
      "text": "\"'But,"
    },
    {
      "start": 916.06,
      "end": 918.74,
      "text": "my dear man,' Gutman objected,"
    },
    {
      "start": 919.328,
      "end": 920.04,
      "text": "\"'can't you see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 920.96,
      "end": 923.42,
      "text": "If I even for a moment thought of doing it—'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 923.968,
      "end": 924.8,
      "text": "\"'But that's ridiculous,"
    },
    {
      "start": 924.98,
      "end": 925.34,
      "text": "too."
    },
    {
      "start": 926.58,
      "end": 930.2,
      "text": "I feel toward Wilmer just exactly as if he were my own son.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 930.94,
      "end": 931.58,
      "text": "I really do.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 932.33,
      "end": 935.7,
      "text": "But if I even for a moment thought of doing what you propose,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 936.14,
      "end": 937.52,
      "text": "what in the world do you"
    },
    {
      "start": 937.52,
      "end": 939.46,
      "text": "think would keep Wilmer from telling the police"
    },
    {
      "start": 939.46,
      "end": 942.48,
      "text": "every last detail about the Falcon and about"
    },
    {
      "start": 942.54,
      "end": 944.15,
      "text": "you and me and all of us?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 945.44,
      "end": 947.04,
      "text": "Spade grinned with stiff lips.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 948.52,
      "end": 950.54,
      "text": "\"'If we had to,' he said softly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 950.76,
      "end": 953.18,
      "text": "\"'we could have him killed resisting arrest."
    },
    {
      "start": 954.18,
      "end": 955.8,
      "text": "But we wouldn't have to go that far.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 956.66,
      "end": 957.78,
      "text": "Let him talk his head off.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 958.4,
      "end": 961.14,
      "text": "I promise you nobody'll do anything about it.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 961.888,
      "end": 963.424,
      "text": "That's easy enough to fix.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 963.94,
      "end": 967.46,
      "text": "The pink flesh on Gutman's forehead crawled in a frown."
    },
    {
      "start": 968.22,
      "end": 969.22,
      "text": "He lowered his head,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 969.34,
      "end": 970.06,
      "text": "mashing his"
    },
    {
      "start": 970.16,
      "end": 971.54,
      "text": "chins together over his collar,"
    },
    {
      "start": 971.7,
      "end": 972.5,
      "text": "and asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 972.86,
      "end": 973.32,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "start": 974.8,
      "end": 977.08,
      "text": "Then with an abruptness that set all his fat",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 977.08,
      "end": 979.16,
      "text": "bulbs to quivering and tumbling against one"
    },
    {
      "start": 979.28,
      "end": 979.48,
      "text": "another,"
    },
    {
      "start": 979.62,
      "end": 980.92,
      "text": "he raised his head,"
    },
    {
      "start": 981.36,
      "end": 982.82,
      "text": "squirmed around to look at the boy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 982.92,
      "end": 983.9,
      "text": "and laughed merrily."
    }
  ]
}